This paper combines model-free Q-learning with model-based Monte-Carlo Tree Search (MCTS) to improve performance in challenging physical reasoning tasks and Atari. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Robotics (cs.RO), Computer Vision (cs.CV), and Graphics (cs.GR).
